These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-1::.
There 7 different types of food: spinach, grapefruit, pear, tomato, kiwi, pineapple, papaya
1. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
2. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person eating tomato##1
3. the person eating papaya is on the left of the person eating pear##1
4. the person eating kiwi is between the person eating spinach and the person eating pear##2
5. the person eating tomato is between the person eating grapefruit and the person eating spinach##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3   |    4    |  5  |   6   |   7   |
| Food   | papaya | pear | kiwi | spinach | tomato | grapefruit | pineapple |

