.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: january, july, october, december, march, august, april
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
4. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's birthday is in january##2
5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
6. the person who's birthday is in october is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |   3    |   4   |     5      |    6    |     7      |
| Birthday   | august | april | january | october | december | july | march |

