.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-3::.
7 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, rat, turtle, hamster, horse, goat
1. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
2. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
4. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
6. the owner of the hamster is between the owner of the horse and the owner of the goldfish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| Pet   | goat | horse | hamster | goldfish | chinchilla | rat | turtle |

