.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-4::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: bellflower, daffodil, lily, daisy, sunflower, poppy, zinnia
1. the person who growszinnia is between the person who growsdaisy and the person who growssunflower##2
2. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
3. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
4. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
5. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
6. the person who growszinnia is in the middle##1
7. the person who growslily is the person who growslily##1
8. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who growslily##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3    |      4      |    5    |    6    |    7    |
| Flower   | poppy | daffodil | daisy | zinnia | sunflower | bellflower | lily |

