.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-20::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: ivory, lilac, green, emerald, apricot, ebony, blood-red
1. the person who likes blood-red is in the middle##1
2. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
3. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
4. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
5. the person who likes emerald is between the person who likes blood-red and the person who likes green##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |   3    |    4    |     5      |   6    |  7  |
| Color   | ivory | lilac | apricot | blood-red | emerald | green | ebony |

 